<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
<style>
  /* Warning Red for permanent deletion */
  .body { font-family: 'Helvetica', Arial, sans-serif; background-color: #fef2f2; padding: 20px; }
  .card { max-width: 500px; background: #ffffff; margin: 0 auto; border-radius: 8px; overflow: hidden; border: 1px solid #fecaca; }
  .header { background-color: #ef4444; padding: 30px; text-align: center; }
  .content { padding: 30px; text-align: center; color: #1f2937; line-height: 1.6; }
  .footer { font-size: 12px; color: #9ca3af; text-align: center; padding: 20px; }
  .warning-box { background: #fff1f2; border: 1px dashed #f43f5e; padding: 15px; margin: 20px 0; border-radius: 4px; color: #991b1b; font-size: 14px; }
</style>
</head>
<body class="body">
  <div class="card">
    <div class="header">
      <img src="{{logoUrl}}" width="100" alt="{{company}} Logo">
    </div>
    <div class="content">
      <h2 style="color: #991b1b;">Confirm Account Deletion</h2>
      <p>Hi {{firstName}},</p>
      <p>We received a request to permanently delete your <strong>{{company}}</strong> account.</p>
      <div class="warning-box">
        <strong>Warning:</strong> This action is permanent. All your data, including profile info and history, will be removed forever after 30 days.
      </div>
      <p>If you didn't request this, please secure your account immediately.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="footer">If you have questions, contact our support team. <br> © {{year}} {{company}}</div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
